name: Titan Strider
notes: Tank Buster: Deals increasing damage to the same target (+2/hit) (assume 6 stacks) | 6 * 2 = 12

name: Mutalisk
notes: Glaive: Attack bounces twice (50% less damage per bounce)

name: Medic
notes: Healing Aura: Heals nearby allies for 3 HP/s (assume 20s heal)

name: Goliath
notes: Damage Aura: Nearby allies gain 8% damage (does not stack)

name: Baneling
notes: Volatile Explosive: Explodes on contact damaging all enemies within 2.5 range (assume 7 hits, but only 1 attack over 30s = 7/30 = 0.23 multiplier)

name: Immortal
notes: Armor Aura: Allies ignore 5 damage per attack (does not stack)

name: Blood Beetle
notes: Proboscis: Attacks embed spines that slow movement by 75% for 6 seconds

name: Siege Tank
notes: Tank Decimator: +6 dmg/hit (assume 8 stacks) | 6*8=48

name: Hydralisk
notes: Poison Attack: Target attacks 20% slower and takes 15 damage over 3 seconds

name: Aberration Basher
notes: Resistance Aura: Allies gain 15% damage reduction => 118% hp

name: Powermortal
notes: Improved Parts: Rapidly regenerates life (7 hp/s) | Assume 15s | survival = 105 HP

name: Hellion
notes: Sunder Attack: Target takes 20% more damage over 10 seconds.

name: Feederling
notes: 30% lifesteal: 150 damage; assume 10 attacks => 0.3*150*10=450

name: High Templar
notes: Bloodlust: One ally attacks and moves 20% faster

name: Broodlord
notes: Spawn Broodlings: 2 broodlings (30 hp, 30 damage) / 1s | Assume 30s wave  = 30 * 2 * 30 HP = 1800 HP

name: Banshee
notes: Explosive Attack: 100% splash damage (assume 3 enemies hit)

name: Hunterling
notes: Hunters Pounce: Jumps towards the target reducing damage of nearby enemies by 30% | assume 50% of attackers hit => 0.3*0.5=0.15DR => 118% HP

name: Ultralisk
notes: War Stomp: Crushes the target and all units behind for 37 damage once every 2 attacks. | 37 dmg * 10 hits / 2 attacks = 185 dmg/attack

name: Aberration Pulverizer
notes: Massive Sweep: Attacks all enemies within reach (assume 4 enemies hit)

name: Thor
notes: Cripple: Target attacks and moves 20% slower while losing 65 HP/s for 6 seconds (assume only 3 seconds of Cripple)

name: Flame Behemoth
notes: Scorching Circle: While 6+ foes are within attack range, inflicts 150 damage/s to enemies within 4 range. (assume 6 enemies struck 50% of the time)

name: Tyrannozor
notes: Thorn Armor: Reflects 180% of non-melee damage back to the attacker (minimum 90 damage). Assume 50% HP (6k) reflected over 20s
